#text=The previous night and this morning before work I noticed I was missing a lot of necessary ingredients for my future meals .
#text=I planned out a trip to the grocery store immediately after work .
#text=After I finished working I drove over to the store .
#text=It was very crowded but not too hard to find a parking spot .
#text=Once inside the store , I grabbed the nearest shopping cart and smiled as one of the grocery workers welcomed me in .
#text=Once inside and out of everyone 's way , I thought about what I needed .
#text=Since I did n't have a list written down , it took me a few minutes .
#text=Once I came up with the list in my head , I started to map out a route in my head that would take the least amount of time for me to follow in the store .
#text=They offered me some free samples of the meat I asked for .
#text=Then I picked up my bread which was right nearby .
#text=At the back wall of the store I found the meat I was going to cook tonight .
#text=After that , I grabbed a few extra items that I thought might also be nice later this week while heading towards checkout .
#text=Luckily , there was n't a line and this was done quickly .
#text=I paid with my debit card and left with all my groceries in a cart , packed them into my car , and headed home .
